column2: "<%me>! Have you seen Zeno? Oh, you haven't?"
"Darn it, he left me behind again!"
"He always does that on dangerous quests! He always leaves me behind!"
"He thinks he's protecting me, but it really ticks me off!"
"It makes me feel like I'm useless to him..."
"If I'm not around, then there's no one to stop Zeno from getting himself killed..."
"Once he gets back, I'm really gonna give him a piece of my mind!"
"Alright, I'm going to head back. Bye bye."
